ing: 12 cocktail franks, cut lengthwise in half
des: "Ritz crackers are topped with slices of cocktail franks and sweet pickle relish with a dab of mustard for a quick, party or gameday snack."
ins:
Arrange franks, cut side down, in a single layer on a microwaveable plate.
Microwave on HIGH 20 seconds or until heated through.
Top crackers with relish, frank pieces and mustard.
